<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Postcard (5 cents). Postmark: ‘’SGRAVENHAGE 7-8 N / 2 MEI 82’. It is addressed to ‘Monsieur Th. van Gogh./ 25 Rue de Laval./ <hi rend="italics">Paris.</hi>’ Van Gogh presumably wrote in English to make it difficult for others to read; cf. in this respect <ref target="let233.xml">letter 233</ref>.</p>
                                    
                                
                    	</note>
                    
